Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.71,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíte Raum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:16.09,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoriť takto o vzorke, to nie ste vy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:19.04,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie som ja, čo?
